OL,3,CFormer mayor charged with bribery and
OL,4,Cmisconduct in public office
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney reports on the Liverpool
OL,8,Fcorruption probe.
OL,10,FThe former Mayor of Liverpool has been
OL,11,Fcharged with bribery, and misconduct
OL,12,Fin a public office.
OL,14,FJoe Anderson, 67, who was first
OL,15,Farrested in December 2020, is among 12
OL,16,Fpeople who have been charged with the
OL,17,Foffences relating to Liverpool City
OL,18,FCouncil contracts between 2010 and
OL,19,F2020.
