OL,3,CFormer mayor charged with bribery and
OL,4,Cmisconduct in public office
OL,6,FDerek Hatton, 77, who was Deputy
OL,7,FLeader of the council in the 1980s,
OL,8,Fhas been charged with bribery and one
OL,9,Fcount of counsel or procure misconduct
OL,10,Fin a public office.
OL,12,FFormer Director of Regeneration
OL,13,FNicholas Kavanagh, 56, and former
OL,14,FAssistant Director Andrew Barr, 51,
OL,15,Fwho was the council's assistant
OL,16,Fdirector of highways and planning,
OL,17,Fhave also been charged, alongside
OL,18,FAnderson's son David, 37, Merseyside
OL,19,FPolice said.
