OL,6,FThe force added the charges come
OL,7,F"following an extensive investigation
OL,8,F(Operation Aloft) connected to the
OL,9,Fawarding of commercial and business
OL,10,Fcontracts from Liverpool City Council
OL,11,Fbetween 2010 and 2020".
OL,13,FFollowing the news Anderson took to
OL,14,Fsocial media to maintain his innocence.
OL,16,FIn a statement posted on his X
OL,17,Faccount, he said: "I am innocent of
OL,18,Fcharges and will fight to clear my
OL,19,Fname. Thank you for all the messages
OL,20,Fof support and best wishes."
