OL,6,FEach will appear at Preston
OL,7,FMagistrates on 28 March.
OL,9,FThose charged are:
OL,11,FTen people have been charged with
OL,12,Fbribery offences committed between
OL,13,F2013 and 2020, concerning advantages
OL,14,Fgiven for the improper awarding of
OL,15,Fcouncil contracts and other services,
OL,16,Fincluding Joe Anderson, Derek Hatton
OL,17,Fand Nicholas Kavanagh.
