OL,3,CFormer mayor charged with bribery and
OL,4,Cmisconduct in public office
OL,6,FRobin Weyell, Deputy Chief Crown
OL,7,FProsecutor said: "The CPS has reviewed
OL,8,Fa full file of evidence from the
OL,9,FMerseyside Police and has authorised
OL,10,Fthe investigation team to charge 12
OL,11,Fpeople with 12 offences related to
OL,12,Fbribery and misconduct in public
OL,13,Foffice."
OL,15,FAnderson, of Knotty Ash, Liverpool,
OL,16,Fwas suspended by the Labour Party
OL,17,Ffollowing his arrest in 2020 and did
OL,18,Fnot stand for re-election the
OL,19,Ffollowing year for the role of Mayor,
OL,20,Fwhich he had held since 2012.
